public abstract class AbstractDrawOptions
extends com.google.gwt.core.client.JavaScriptObject

Abstract base class for all draw options. Provides methods for setting options with arbitrary names. If options are added to a Google Visualization that are not yet supported by the GWT wrapper for that visualization, the caller can call these "unstructured" methods to set the new option.
